quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  11,20,"∆Åen siforii…ìe …óin sifaaji, …ìe laatanooki hattan…ìe laa- wagol lepte Alla …óen ka leydi si …óe jippike e ma…ì…ìe. Alanaa…ìe kadi yi…ó…ìe wallondirtee…ìe gaanin Alla ko du√±ana …ìe Makko …óen. Lepte …óen sowoyte …ìe √ëal- √ëalnde Darngal sabu ko …ìe wo…ó…óitori …ìe laatanoo-ki wo…ó…óintini wo…ó…ìe goo e laawol Alla ngol. ∆Åe laa- tanooki hattan…ìe nanoo…ìe ja…ìa goonga e peewal, …ìewa wonaano kadi yi'oo…ìe taskoo Aayeeje Alla …óen ka Winndere, tawde ko …ìe lunndorinoo…ìe goonga kan ko tii…ói."
  11,21,"Ko …ìen siforii…ìe …óin sifaaji woni sooyim…ìe ko'e mun naadugol …óe e halkaare sabu ko …ìe kafidi(renndini) kon e Alla. Kon ko …ìe luurunoo e kafidetee…ói e tefooji majjiri …ìe."
  11,22,"Sikke alaa wonnde …ìen …óon √ëalnde Darngal, ko kam…ìe …ìuroyta sooyude, tawde …ìe wa…ótitirii liimanaaku ngun keeferaaku, laakara on aduna, yurmeende nden lepte."
  11,23,"∆Åen gom…óim…ìe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, …ìe yankinanni Alla, ko …ìen woni yim…ìe Aljanna …ìen, kam…ìe ko…ìe duumotoo…ìe ton poomaa."
  11,24,"Misal feddeji …ói…ói …óin ka heefere…ìe e ka gom…óim…ìe: ko wano bun…óo mo yi'ataa, e faa…óu…óo mo nanataa, …óum ko misal heefer…ìe …ìen …ìe nanatah ja…ìa goonga, …ìe yi'atah …ìe taskoo ko nafata …ìe. Misal goo ko nanoowo e yi'oowo, ko …ìen woni misal fedde gom…óim…ìe …ìen hawtu…ìe nanugol yi'a. E nee, …óin feddeeji …ói…ói no fata sifa e fiyaaku? ∆Åe fotatah. E on waajitotaako e kon ko …ìe fotatah?"
  11,25,"Gom…óii Men Nulii Nuuhu e yim…ìe makko …ìen, o maakani …ìe: ko onon yo yim…ìe, min komi jertinoowo on e lepte Alla, …ìannginan…óo on komi Nulaa kon e moo…óon."
  11,26,"Mi…óo nodda on e rewugol Alla tun, hara on rewaali si wanaa Kanko. Min mi…óo hulani on lepte √±alaande muusunde."
  11,27,"Mbatu teddu…ìe e hooree…ìe yeddu…ìe …ìen ka yim…ìe makko wi'i: Men noototaako noddaandu maa; tawde a hanndaa e huunde, an ko a …ìanndinke sifa amen, e tawde kadi men yi'aali …ìen jokku…ìe ma si wanaa jaasu…ìe amen e ko fee√±ani men e gii…óe, tawde kadi on …ìeydoraa teddungal e jawdi e jaahu ko men jokkira on. Worin me…óen sikki on fenoo…ìe e ko noddoton e mun."
  11,28,"Nuuhu maakani …ìe: Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, yeetee lam si tawii mi…óo e …ìanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am ko seeditoo e goonga am; wa…ó…óina on googingol lam, O ye…óii lam yurmeende Annabaaku e Nuleede immorde ka Makko, …óum wirniraa e mon majjeede mon …óum, e men waawnay on e gom…óingol nde naada e …ìer…óe mon? Men hattanaaka …óum. Ko Alla tun hawrindinta e gom…óinal."